-dense, high-protein shake that keeps you satisfied for hours. Perfect for days when you don’t feel hungry enough for a full meal but still need quality nutrition.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="956589d2-4e07-4c12-94c6-cd10edbfbd49" class="r-1jxty60" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="3937bf67-30cb-45a8-91be-d64bfa26afc1" aria-controls="replo-:R2fj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1mr7uqa"><div data-rid="57f6a674-4267-46bf-99f4-bcb00e1d552c" class="r-obcp7b alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h3>Can I use TrueFit even if I'm not on GLP-1 medications?</h3></span></div><div data-rid="3a552481-8ae9-4e88-892c-8a049ea5e3c9" class="r-66u105"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1ld97go" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2fj2:"><div data-rid="854a092f-590a-4d5c-bc62-d6c1a75bb3a5" class="r-es7q4o"><div data-rid="8e07e72c-704c-40be-8901-fb8aacbe2b81" class="r-8u9ffj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)">Absolutely. TrueFit works as a natural appetite-supporting, muscle-preserving, clean protein shake for anyone trying to lose weight or improve nutrition.</span></p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="a551f6df-6f9a-42cc-a012-7dbceff17674" class="r-nmq8mr" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="b52cc47f-27d1-44fb-9554-c749c8af2160" aria-controls="replo-:R2vj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-18ouojk"><div data-rid="13cb4f0b-a798-495b-9425-ab5cae6d452a" class="r-1yyyvzx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>When should I take TrueFit?</p></span></div><div data-rid="999c42ec-ba2b-4350-893e-d8e365a3423b" class="r-19lwqrd"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-8qmuiz" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div hidden="" id="replo-:R2vj2:"><div data-rid="4c608681-d7d6-464d-98f9-e6107ffb8ced" class="r-1neopki"><div data-rid="26b23ad4-3640-4b27-bf61-aae86678e79d" class="r-576avc alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>TrueFit is designed to fit seamlessly into any weight-loss routine — with or without GLP-1 medications. You can take it any time you need a filling, nutrient-dense option, but most customers prefer it:</p><p><br>Morning: as a balanced, high-protein breakfast that sets the tone for the day<br><br>Midday: as an easy, satisfying lunch replacement<br><br>Post-Workout: to support lean muscle and recovery<br><br>On low-appetite days: when GLP-1 medications make full meals difficult<br><br>Evenings: as a clean, sweet-tooth-satisfying shake without derailing goals</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="79317dac-5635-4bff-8a80-aaa35193747a" class="r-1rrrl17" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed"><div data-rid="0e805e6d-6b7a-4f0a-a73a-114150b955e9" aria-controls="replo-:R3fj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1vznyfq"><div data-rid="b308b821-068f-4c16-8b02-3d3a1e1b615a" class="r-al4sq1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span>Will TrueFit help preserve muscle while losing weight?</span></p></span></div><div data-rid="6bd2e04b-470f-43bf-a208-e292cf74548d" class="r-1dr6j47"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-5f52yn" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/s